text: Masoud Bakheet (; born 5 January 1992) is a Saudi Arabian professional footballer who plays as a right back for Al-Hazem. ==Club Career== Bakheet started his career with Hetten coming through the youth ranks before being promoted to the first team. On June 25, 2015, Bakheet joined Al-Nahda. He spent a year at the club before signing for Al-Hazem.
